    <h2 style="color: #333; font-weight: bold;">Email Confirmation from Jake Library </h2>
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p>To confirm your email address, please enter the following code:</p>
    <h3 style="color: #666; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">{{confirmationCode}}</h3>
